    "We compute mean complexity",
    "Identifying characteristic words for human a GPT-4 reappraisals.",
    "Taking the semantic analysis one step further, we were interested in whether reappraisal success was associated with concrete and distinct vocabulary instead of language complexity overall.",
    "To this end, we calculated a class-based TFIDF to identify characteristic words for two groups: GPT-4 and human reappraisals.",
    "Class-based TFIDF (term frequency inverse document frequency) concatenates human and GPT-4 reappraisals into two large documents and identifies top words for each group by taking into account the frequency of words within each group, as well as in the corpus overall."
